                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.6131/591: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Thurston</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-08-03T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 3, 1940—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>413. Your 954, August 2, 7 p.m. For your information consideration is still being
                    given to the desirability of including the coal notes in the renewal of the
                    agreement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
